<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span6">
    	<div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide bs-docs-carousel-example">
        	<ol class="carousel-indicators">
          		<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          		<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1"></li>
          		<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          		<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="3"></li>
        	</ol>
        
        	<div class="carousel-inner">
          		<div class="item active">
            		<%= image_tag("poolcleaning wfx.jpg", :size => "631x353") %>
            		<div class="carousel-caption">
            			<p class="pool-caption">
            				Free for homeowners
            			</p>
            			<p>
            				<z class="pool-caption-minor">
	            				<%= link_to "sign-up", new_user_path(role: "propertyowner"), remote: true %> for your account
    						</z>
            			</p>
            		</div>
          		</div>
          		<div class="item">
            		<%= image_tag("landscaping wfx.jpg", :size => "631x353") %>
            		<z class="landscape">
	            		<div class="carousel-caption">    
	            		    <p class="landscape-caption">
	            				Home maintenance service provider?
	            			</p>
	            			<p>
	            				<z class="landscape-caption-minor">
	            					take a <%= link_to "feature tour", feature_tour_path %>, view our <%= link_to "pricing plans", pricing_plans_path %>, and <%= link_to "sign-up", new_user_path(role: "serviceowner"), remote: true %> for an account
	            				</z>
	            			</p>
	            		</div>
	            	</z>
          		</div>
          		<div class="item">
            		<%= image_tag("housecleaning wfx.jpg", :size => "631x353") %>
            		<z class="housecleaner">
	            		<div class="carousel-caption">    
	            		    <p>
		            		    <z class="housecleaner-caption">
		            				Manage multiple properties
		            			</z> 
		            		</p>
	               			<p>
	               				<z class="housecleaner-caption-minor">
		               				ideal for <%= link_to "2nd home owners", new_user_path(role: "propertyowner"), remote: true %>
	   							</z>
	            			</p>
	            		</div>
	            	</z>
          		</div>
          		<div class="item">
            		<%= image_tag("snowplow wfx.jpg", :size => "631x353") %>
            		<z class="snowplow">
	            		<div class="carousel-caption">    
	            		    <p>
		            		    <z class="snowplow-caption">
		            				Remote home service monitoring
		            			</z> 
		            		</p>
	               			<p>
	               				<z class="snowplow-caption-minor">
		               				receive email alerts and verification that services are completed
	   							</z>
	            			</p>
	            		</div>
	            	</z>
          		</div>
        	</div>
        

        	<a class="carousel-control left" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="prev">‹</a>
  			<a class="carousel-control right" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="next">›</a>
    	</div>
	</div>
	<div class="span6" id="logo-and-buttons">
		<center>
			<br>
			<%= image_tag("logo.jpg", alt: "HumbleCasa logo", size: "173x59") %>
			<z id="main-title">
				<h1>Welcome to HumbleCasa!</h1>
				<h2>...simplify your home maintenance</h2>
			</z>
			<br>
			<div class="row-fluid">	
				<div class="span6">
					<%= render 'shared/login_link'%>
				</div>
				<div class="span6">
					<h5>New to the site? Sign-up:</h5>
					<z class="launch-user-form">
						<%= link_to new_user_path(role: "propertyowner"), remote: true, class: "btn btn-warning" do %>
							<i class="icon-user icon-white"></i> New property owner account
						<% end %>
					</z>
				</div>
			</div>
			<br>		
		</center>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span12">
		<p>
			HumbleCasa is the <b>free</b> and easy way to <b>schedule</b> and <b>track</b> home maintenance requests. See all of your maintenance requests in one place (house cleaners, landscapers, pool cleaners, etc.) and receive <b>verification</b> that the requested home services have been completed!
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				Receive email notifications with pictures from your service provider when each service request is complete 
			</li>
			<li>
				HumbleCasa will verify the accuracy of these reports, giving you confidence that your home is in top shape
			</li>
			<li>
				Ideal for 2nd home owners who need to remotely turn properties around for future rentals or visitors, or anybody with a busy lifestyle that isn't always home to check up on their home service providers
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Create an account, register with your service providers, and manage your house from your computer or smartphone <b>all for free!</b></p>
	</div>
</div>
<br>

<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span12">
		<center><p class="service-notification">
			<b>Do you own a company that provides home maintainence services?</b><br> We can help you to connect with your customers, manage your workforce, and simplify both invoicing and payroll. Visit our <%= link_to "Service Provider page", business_path %> to get more details and sign up.
		</p></center>
	</div>
</div>
